---

## Part of a Larger Platform

This pod integrates with:

| Pod | Connection |
|---|---|
| Candidate Experience | Receives candidate profile and application actions |
| AI Matchmaking | Receives matched job suggestions to track |
| Assessment & Intelligence | Receives assessment results and deadlines |
| Recruiter Platform | Sends interview schedules and candidate status |
| Shared Systems & Ops | Firebase auth, shared database, notifications |

